                            <code>obj_id</code>, <code>obj_type</code>, <code>created_time </code>
                            and <code>deleted_time</code>.
                        </para>
                    </wadl:doc>
                </param>
                <param name="sort_dir" style="query" required="false">
                    <wadl:doc xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:lang="EN">
                        <para>The sort direction of the webhook list.  Either <code>asc</code>
                            (ascending) or <code>desc</code> (descending) is acceptable.
                        </para>
                    </wadl:doc>
                </param>
                <param name="global_tenant" style="query" required="false">
                    <wadl:doc xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:lang="EN">
                        <para>Indicates whether webhooks from all tenants(projects) are listed.
                            This operation is subject to access privilege constraints.</para>
                    </wadl:doc>
